-- RHJ Is Still Interested in Buying BHF-Bank, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   K a r i n   M a t u s s e k
-- 2012-04-02T06:10:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-02/rhj-is-still-interested-in-buying-bhf-bank-handelsblatt-says.html
RHJ International (RHJI)  is still
interested in buying  Deutsche Bank AG (DBK) ’s BHF-Bank unit,
Handelsblatt reported, citing Leonhard Fischer, RHJ’s chief
executive officer.  While Deutsche Bank and RHJ have been negotiating for nine
months, no formal request for approval of a possible takeover
has been sent to Bafin,  Germany ’s financial regulator, the
newspaper said, citing unidentified people close to the talks.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karin Matussek in Berlin at 
 kmatussek@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Aarons at 
 aaarons@Bloomberg.net . 